AIX-Perfstat version 0.01
=========================

This module is intended as a wrapper around the functionality exposed in the
libperfstat library on AIX. The module has been compiled with GCC and tested 
on AIX 5.1.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

	libperfstat.so - Available from AIX install media as bos.perf.libperfstat.bff 

